document_data.name: [[Jamaldro]]
document_data.mainbody: '''Jamaldro''' was the cellarer of [[Castle Obarskyr]] in [[Suzail]] in the late 15{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Relationships: A number of nobles knew his name.
document_data.History: Jamaldro was working during the [[Open Feast]] held at [[Castle Obarskyr]] in [[Mirtul 26]] of the {{yearlinkName|1479}}.{{cite book/Elminster Must Die/MMP|73|7}}
